* Axis X (Stick and Directional Pad) = Horizontal Joystick
* Axis Y (Stick and Directional Pad) = Vertial Joystick
* 
* Triangle = Joystick Button 0
* Circle = Joystick Button 1
* Cross = Joystick Button 2
* Square = Joystick Button 3
* 
* L1 = Joystick Button 4
* R1 = Joystick Button 5
* L2 = Joystick Button 6
* R2 = Joystick Button 7
* L3 = Joystick Button 10
* R3 = Joystick Button 11
* 
* Select = Joystick Button 8
* Start = Joystick Button 11
* Playstation = Joystick Button 12